        "Ruins of the Empire"
      ],
      "text": "Ruins of the Empire\u00a0is an upcoming graphic novel trilogy set in the Avatar universe, directly following the events of\u00a0the Turf Wars trilogy. It will be the second series based on\u00a0The Legend of Korra and is written by franchise co-creator\u00a0Michael Dante DiMartino, with art by Michelle Wong and Vivian Ng. The first issue is set to be released on May 21, 2019."
    },
